About Us

Our Mission

The August 93 Club, also known as Ohanze Congress, was established with a vision to unite our community and preserve our rich cultural heritage. We are dedicated to service for advancement of all members.

Our Vision

To foster community development, preserve cultural traditions, and empower our members through education, collaboration, and sustainable initiatives that benefit everyone.

Our Values

Unity, Progress, Heritage, Excellence, and Community Service form the cornerstone of everything we do at August 93 Club - Ohanze Congress.
